text: haey chea karpit nasa yeung doeng tha puokke( puok mou sh ri- ki n) pitchea nung niyeay tha tampit anak del bangrien ke( mou ha- meat) kreante chea mnoussa thommotea bonnaoh . pheasaea del puokke chaot brakean ke chea pheasaea phe sang haey( kompir kuor an) nih chea pheasaea areab yeang chbasaleasa
